  "keyFeatures": [
    "Photo and video capture with configurable quality, codec, and bitrate",
    "QR/barcode scanning via native iOS APIs and Android MLKit",
    "Realtime frame processors using JSI worklets at 60+ FPS",
    "Skia-powered drawing and filters directly on camera frames",
    "Multi-camera and virtual device support (wide, ultra-wide, telephoto)",
    "Customizable camera formats, FPS (up to 240), HDR, and stabilization",
    "Smooth zooming with Reanimated integration",
    "Exposure, focus, and orientation controls",
    "Expo config plugin support",
    "GPS location tagging for photos"
  ],
